Take it easy.

40:37.834 --> 40:39.291
What about him?

40:39.375 --> 40:42.125
Is that your
boyfriend?

40:42.208 --> 40:43.583
I think so.

40:43.667 --> 40:46.083
Yeah.

40:46.166 --> 40:47.333
I can tell he's smart.

40:47.417 --> 40:49.166
Oh, my God, honestly,

40:49.250 --> 40:50.750
I think he's the smartest
person I've ever met.

40:50.834 --> 40:52.166
Mom called
him "ghetto."

40:52.250 --> 40:53.834
So offensive.

40:53.917 --> 40:55.750
Yeah, well, what do you think
your dad was

40:55.834 --> 40:56.875
when she met him?

40:56.959 --> 40:58.417
Really?

40:58.500 --> 41:00.000
Yeah.

41:00.083 --> 41:02.750
He wn't the suave individual
he is today.

41:02.834 --> 41:05.667
♪ Let me go... ♪

41:05.750 --> 41:07.834
MARVIN:
Yeah, one, two, three.
You go...

41:07.917 --> 41:09.125
one, two, three.

41:09.208 --> 41:10.542
That's good.
I can't do that.

41:10.625 --> 41:13.834
♪ Let me go. ♪

41:13.917 --> 41:16.291
(muffled music playing)

41:25.333 --> 41:27.709
(sniffs)

41:34.125 --> 41:36.208
♪ ♪

41:53.291 --> 41:56.333
(flame crackling)

42:05.041 --> 42:06.250
(indistinct conversations)

42:06.333 --> 42:08.792
♪ Talking 'bout the music ♪

42:09.500 --> 42:12.625
♪ Talking 'bout the music ♪

42:21.041 --> 42:24.000
Hey, Bunchy!

42:24.083 --> 42:26.208
(laughing)

42:26.291 --> 42:28.583
MICKEY:
How you doing, Bunch? Huh?

42:28.667 --> 42:29.834
How'd it go,
Bunch?

42:30.500 --> 42:32.667
Hey, kiddo, you all right?

42:32.750 --> 42:35.625
Huh?

42:37.542 --> 42:38.500
What did you do?

42:38.583 --> 42:39.792
No, let it burn.

42:39.875 --> 42:40.792
What did you do?

42:40.875 --> 42:41.291
Jesus!
Oh, shit.

42:41.375 --> 42:43.667
There's a fire!

42:43.750 --> 42:45.375
MAN:
Yeah, it's upstairs.
Come on. Let's go.

42:45.458 --> 42:46.750
Let's go. Come on.

42:46.834 --> 42:49.041
WOMAN:
All right. All right.

42:49.125 --> 42:51.625
(indistinct chatter,
music playing)

42:53.583 --> 42:56.291
(sobbing):
Just get out, all of you!

42:56.375 --> 42:58.834
Get out of fucking my shithole!

43:04.333 --> 43:06.792
(phone ringing)

43:11.917 --> 43:12.917
Hey, Terry, what's up?

43:13.000 --> 43:16.208
TERRY:
Uh, Bunchy got real upset
about something,

43:16.291 --> 43:17.834
and there's been a small fire.

43:17.917 --> 43:19.917
What do you want me
to do about it?

43:20.000 --> 43:23.709
It's under control now, but...

43:23.792 --> 43:25.834
Ray, look...

43:25.917 --> 43:28.500
Conor and Bridget are here.

43:35.583 --> 43:37.333
(Mickey exhales)

43:37.417 --> 43:40.250
How you feeling? Better?

43:46.625 --> 43:48.041
(car door opens)

43:55.834 --> 43:55.959
Get in the car.

43:59.500 --> 44:01.875
Get in the car, Conor, now.
TERRY: Ray...

44:01.959 --> 44:03.500
Now!
TERRY:
Everybody's all right.

44:06.542 --> 44:08.959
He didn't
do nothing.

44:11.041 --> 44:11.667
Hey, Ray Ray, take it easy.

44:11.750 --> 44:13.291
If you're angry at me, fine.

44:13.375 --> 44:14.458
He's just a little boy.

44:14.542 --> 44:16.792
Where's your sister?

44:16.875 --> 44:17.500
I don't know.

44:17.583 --> 44:19.667
Look, I'm sorry
I didn't go

44:19.750 --> 44:21.500
to more of your
football games.

44:35.417 --> 44:37.041
TERRY:
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

44:37.125 --> 44:38.166
Ray, Ray, Ray,
it wasn't his fault.

44:38.250 --> 44:39.083
It just got out of hand!

44:39.166 --> 44:40.917
MICKEY:
Come on, Ray,
put that down.

44:41.000 --> 44:41.333
There's witnesses here.

44:41.417 --> 44:44.417
Your children.

44:53.834 --> 44:56.000
You might've had the balls
to put me away, kid,

44:56.083 --> 44:57.166
but shoot me?

44:57.250 --> 44:58.709
I don't think so.

45:06.041 --> 45:07.625
(grunts)

45:07.709 --> 45:09.333
Grandpa.

45:10.500 --> 45:12.959
(engine starts)

45:13.041 --> 45:14.625
(tires squeal)

45:14.709 --> 45:16.000
Get in the car, honey.

45:16.083 --> 45:16.417
You, too, Conor.

45:16.500 --> 45:18.834
(gun cocks)

45:20.041 --> 45:21.041
TERRY:
Put the fucking gun down!

45:24.291 --> 45:26.333
(chuckles softly)

45:27.542 --> 45:30.625
Daddy, please stop it!

45:30.709 --> 45:31.917
Daddy...

45:32.000 --> 45:35.041
BRIDGET (crying):
Please... stop...

45:48.875 --> 45:50.000
Come on.

45:51.208 --> 45:54.083
Now.

45:56.375 --> 45:58.083
Get in the fucking car!
Stop!

45:58.166 --> 45:58.500
Raymond!

45:58.583 --> 46:00.417
(sobbing)

46:00.500 --> 46:02.500
I'll take them.

46:02.583 --> 46:05.500
(siren wails in distance)

46:05.583 --> 46:07.208
Frances has
got a car.

46:07.291 --> 46:09.041
We'll get 'em home.
They'll be fine.

46:11.250 --> 46:13.000
But you got to calm down.

46:13.083 --> 46:14.250
(sirens approaching)

46:14.333 --> 46:16.041
And you got to get out of here.

46:35.667 --> 46:38.250
(sobbing)

47:07.875 --> 47:09.250
(exhales)

47:09.333 --> 47:11.083
Hello, Raymond.

47:17.875 --> 47:19.250
How you feeling?

47:19.333 --> 47:23.125
Happy to be alive, darling.

47:31.834 --> 47:33.000
What's on your mind, Raymond?

47:36.792 --> 47:38.750
(exhales)

47:38.834 --> 47:40.125
I don't know.

47:44.458 --> 47:45.834
I don't know anymore.

47:45.917 --> 47:48.250
Raymond...

47:50.041 --> 47:52.333
My father.

47:55.041 --> 47:58.291
He's been causing us trouble
since he arrived.

47:58.792 --> 48:01.166
You'll handle it.

48:03.083 --> 48:04.291
No, I won't.

48:09.667 --> 48:11.000
It's over, Ezra.

48:24.166 --> 48:26.000
He's working with the FBI.

48:30.625 --> 48:32.709
(sighs)

48:33.375 --> 48:36.709
I see.

48:40.750 --> 48:43.667
Well...

48:43.750 --> 48:45.333
we're gonna have to kill him.

48:57.250 --> 48:59.542
It's not that simple.

49:03.250 --> 49:05.834
He's still my father.

49:07.166 --> 49:08.166
Hmm.

49:13.125 --> 49:15.417
(exhales)

49:17.083 --> 49:19.208
So...

49:22.458 --> 49:26.291
Who hates him more than we do?

49:32.208 --> 49:34.041
(TV audience applauding,
music plays)

49:34.125 --> 49:35.041
(man and woman laughing)

49:35.125 --> 49:37.792
♪ We've got laughs
from coast to coast ♪

49:37.875 --> 49:40.583
♪ To make you smile ♪

49:40.667 --> 49:42.834
♪ A real-life look
at each of you ♪

49:42.917 --> 49:45.959
♪ To capture all that style ♪

49:46.041 --> 49:48.542
♪ You're the red,
white and blue ♪

49:48.625 --> 49:51.000
♪ The funny things you do ♪
(laughing loudly)

49:51.083 --> 49:55.500
♪ America, America,
this is you ♪

49:57.709 --> 50:00.875
♪ Stories from
your friends next door ♪

50:00.959 --> 50:02.709
♪ They never told ♪
Look at this guy!

50:02.792 --> 50:05.083
♪ You might be a star tonight ♪
He does it
a second time!

50:05.166 --> 50:07.583
♪ So let that camera roll ♪

50:07.667 --> 50:09.417
♪ You're the red,
white and blue... ♪
